definition: Wuhu prefecture level city in Anhui

sentences.english: The fourth chapter researches on the perceptions of farmers losing land in Wuhu city.
sentences.chinese: 第四章是蕪湖市失地農民的感知分析。

sentences.english: The density of SO2 in atmosphere of Wuhu city was predicted with the model.
sentences.chinese: 再用該模型對蕪湖市大氣中SO2的濃度進行預測。

sentences.english: Conclusions Wuhu city had got the anticipated effect by implementing the modern tuberculosis control strategy.
sentences.chinese: 結論蕪湖市實施的現代結核病控制策略有較好效果。
